# A form of [[error]] arising from mishearing a [[spoken]] or [[sung]] [[phrase]]
#:'''Examples:'''
#:* “The ants are my friends, blowin’ in the wind.” (“The answer, my friend, is...”) from [[w:Bob Dylan|Bob Dylan's]] “Blowin' In the Wind.”
